FILTER.PATIENT_STATUS_DESCRIPTION.CAREPL: Active - Patients with 1 or more current/completed care plans
Registered - Patients for whom care plans need to be assigned
Not Onboarded - Potential patients who we reached out to, but weren't interested / didn't consent to any of the programs
Discharged - Patients who have completed 1 or more care plans and no longer need medical assistance
FILTER.PATIENT_STATUS_DESCRIPTION.EPISOD: Active - Patients with 1 or more current/completed episodes
Registered - Patients for whom episodes need to be set up
Not Onboarded - Potential patients who we reached out to, but weren't interested / didn't consent to any of the programs
Suspended - Patients who are suspended from the program temporarily
Flagged For Disqualification - Patients who are flagged due to not matching the qualification criteria
Discharged - Patients who have completed 1 or more episodes and no longer need medical assistance
